reviews.text:
Horrible service, feels like I’m gonna get yelled at by the waitress anytime. Found a dead cockroach on the floor, informed the waitress and she doesn’t feel sorry at all. Feel like it’s a super normal thing to open up restaurant with cockroach on the floor. 

Only thing that taste ok is the noodles. The 炸兩’s skin is so thick and the 甜醫 (sweet sauce) taste very weird. 

Overall: DONT COME UNLESS ITS THE ONLY RESTAURANT OPEN IN THE MORNING
